Nabil Halfaoui Comment on the top of the basket: Thank you, Bebo .. But a farce
05 Nov 2019, 10:17 by Mustafa Karam
Mustafa Karam commented the artist Nabil Al-Halafawi on the victory of Al-Ahly club Zamalek, the result of 92_80 in the 16th round of the Egyptian Basketball Cup and the clash of the players after the game. "Congratulations to Al-Ahly to beat Zamalek 92-80 in the Egyptian Basketball Cup and qualify for the quarter-finals," Nabil El-Halafawi tweeted on Twitter. "Thank you to the board and Captain Khatib for supporting the team with deals that have achieved the full control that we witnessed today, and deeply regretted the sports farce during the game to withdraw as the difference widened (3 times) and the battle after the end." It is very unfortunate; I wish you could see a solution for this withdrawals team. Congratulations to our Lord and success in Elly Guy. " Clash with players Al - Ahli Some highlight the player 's skills, which aroused the anger of Zamalek players and clash with Al - Ahli players.
